will be deleted in the normal course of business pursuant to our current
data retention practices. You may request to have all your personal
information deleted by contacting

deletion requests to the extent permissible by law and will not delete
data that we are legally required to maintain (such as data subject to a
current and valid preservation order or transaction data required for
audit purposes).

permits our users who are California residents to request certain
information regarding our disclosure of personal information to

Group, Inc. 100 Union Square Drive, New Hope, PA 18938 or by email
at support@themeetgroup.com. Please be advised that we are only
required to respond to one request per user each year.

web sites or online services. We may allow third parties, such as
